Cristiano Ronaldo scored the equaliser but was not able to lead his side to victory at the Nou Camp

Sportsmail's Rik Sharma awarded PIque 9/10 for his 'world-class' performance against Real Madrid.

He said: 'This was a performance from the defender which some believed was beyond him after his fall from grace. Got his head to every ball when it mattered and executed some perfect tackles.'

